{"tid":1428580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［全部發夢嘅人入一入黎］黑狗戰術進化左","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:17:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T19:02:30.000Z","uid":81586,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5aeb89b008cc28e831aaa7f8b2ef1e69097b16f","tid":1428580,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:17:14.000Z","msg":"尋晚發夢聽前線講尋晚黑警有新招數<br />\n1.用便衣混入前線，有需要時拖住義士。<br />\n<br />\n2.當你發覺條內街黑媽媽，又見到狗車冇著燈，<br />\n其實唔代表入面冇狗，入面可能有狗會等你行近狗車就落車咬人，咬人嘅係畜龍黎，所以速度未必夠佢地快<br />\n<br />\n3.黑警會利用義士同情心比救護車同消防車入示威區，<br />\n但小心當消防同救護車慢駛離開時，小心後面會有狗跟住車尾慢慢行，到咁上下距離先發現已經太遲<br />\n<br />\n4.小心各個車後同暗角處，黑狗有保護色<br />\n<br />\n5.小心黑狗扮撤退 實際退完就反攻<br />\n<br />\n以上係總結左深水埗晚黑狗嘅新招，各位武運亨通"},{"pid":"5638fc319933078b486f9bbadd0102f95c79079d","tid":1428580,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc337c3f79666624488bad0b54035ea08c45456","tid":1428580,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:32:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facd9fb5efb673c61b88973efa98a4b589b49544","tid":1428580,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6d50921c9b191c45aec527840a15c166cd8887","tid":1428580,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3672b32a25e6404788ab87242887066b9659a0","tid":1428580,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:45:18.000Z","msg":"咁都有人負評？"},{"pid":"07d11bd335ca028bc44f72bdae2f32ade0e0524c","tid":1428580,"uid":81586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T11:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces